Class JournalCollection

  • java.lang.Object
    • unidue.ub.statistics.media.journal.JournalCollection
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    @Entity
public class JournalCollection
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Comparable<JournalCollection>
    Plain old java object as representation of a journal collection, collecting all JournalTitles (by their issn) contained in this collection
